00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:53,420
as a refutation to clarify his wrongness.

280
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:57,220
Make equal work and rest as the reason.

281
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:16,860
Aunt,

282
00:15:18,060 --> 00:15:19,740
the princess has passed away for many years,

283
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,260
but madam is still in grief.

284
00:15:22,260 --> 00:15:23,780
Should we try to persuade her

285
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:25,700
to let go of the past.

286
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:30,100
Regardless of the Third or Eighth Princess,

287
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:32,580
Yaoyao passed away so unexpectedly.

288
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:35,100
Madam believed she was

289
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:36,380
murdered by someone.

290
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:38,180
Even till now, she can’t take it.

291
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,540
But it was indeed an accident.

292
00:15:42,260 --> 00:15:44,100
You know I didn’t put the pollen…

293
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,100
Shush, stop talking about it.

294
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:50,820
A few years ago,

295
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:54,060
she thought about tracking down

296
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,060
the escaped maid.

297
00:15:56,540 --> 00:15:57,380
But nowadays,

298
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:58,700
she only mentioned it occasionally.

299
00:15:58,740 --> 00:16:01,100
She’ll forget about it in a few years.

300
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:02,420
So, don’t bring it up anymore.

301
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:04,460
Just

302
00:16:04,580 --> 00:16:06,380
wait to give birth to the child.

303
00:16:06,820 --> 00:16:08,100
Don’t make any mistakes.

304
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:09,740
You have a bright future.

305
00:16:21,660 --> 00:16:23,020
Xia Song’s an able official,

306
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:28,820
not to mention his achievements in the annotation
to classical literature.

307
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:30,740
Looking back now,

308
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,620
I found his proposals on the war against the Xixia,

309
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:36,500
which recommend defending the territory
without active attack,

310
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,100
and locking down the border and cutting off trade,

311
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:40,980
were in fact insightful enough

312
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,540
to nail down the point.

313
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:45,780
But back then,

314
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:49,180
Han Qi and I were young and reckless,

315
00:16:49,700 --> 00:16:52,940
let alone Ouyang Xiu, Cai Xiang,

316
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,180
Su Shunqin and others

317
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:56,780
despised him for his clinging to comfortable life

318
00:16:57,220 --> 00:16:58,260
and fear of the enemy,

319
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:02,100
which made him scorned by gentlemen.

320
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:04,220
Later,

321
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,860
the Ode to Imperial Virtue

322
00:17:08,180 --> 00:17:10,380
confirmed his ill reputation.

323
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:13,500
Ever since then, he did a villain’s deeds,

324
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:16,580
disputing over every trifle,

325
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:18,620
and seeking revenge for the smallest grievance.

326
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:23,220
Though he had official achievements before,

327
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:25,580
other officials despised him

328
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,780
also for his greed, lust,

329
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:28,940
and degradation,

330
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:31,420
without the trait of a gentleman.

331
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:32,820
If the court,

332
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:34,500
or the nation,

333
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,140
has to distinguish the righteous from the evil

334
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:39,140
when discussing official business,

335
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:40,140
and has to distinguish gentlemen from villains

336
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,420
when talking about a person,

337
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:45,820
this will be ganging up

338
00:17:45,820 --> 00:17:46,860
to exclude dissidents for right or wrong.

339
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:49,900
Compared to that for power and fortune,

340
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:51,780
the former one worries me more.

341
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:57,540
I’m reluctant to see a clique of gentlemen

342
00:17:58,060 --> 00:17:59,260
being able to rally multitudes at their call.

343
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:03,820
Your Majesty...

344
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:07,580
The greed for fortune is human nature.

345
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:09,500
Pursuing goodness is also human nature.

346
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:11,500
Both have no fault.

347
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:14,220
But if one cannot keep a balance,

348
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:15,380
becoming stubborn and obstinate,

349
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,300
then he’s evil.

350
00:18:22,660 --> 00:18:24,620
Smuggling salt in violation of ban

351
00:18:24,940 --> 00:18:26,220
was not within the duties of

352
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,020
the Imperial Security Agency,

353
00:18:27,580 --> 00:18:28,500
yet you carried out investigation.

354
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,820
You suspect it was related to some officials,
don’t you?

355
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,300
Back then,
the government strictly locked down the border.

356
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:40,140
There were people from Xixia

357
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:41,900
risking lives for livelihood,

358
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,420
who passed checkpoints

359
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:45,020
and smuggled salt into Song.

360
00:18:45,220 --> 00:18:46,620
Such cases were supposed to be scarce,

361
00:18:47,260 --> 00:18:48,620
yet the amount was large.

362
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:52,300
Officials guarding borders must give them pass

363
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:54,700
so that they could come all the way to the Capital.

364
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:55,780
And I guessed,

365
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:56,980
the one granting pass

366
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:59,660
was a senior official.

367
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,020
You suspected Xia Song?

368
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:06,340
Yes.

369
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:08,780
Any evidence?

370
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,980
The case of smuggling salt

371
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:13,700
was presumed based on circumstantial evidence.

372
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:14,900
I firmly believed that

373
00:19:15,060 --> 00:19:16,780
Xia Song abused
his power to do such illegal business.

374
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:20,020
But after investigation over a year,

375
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:22,220
I failed to get any evidence.

376
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:27,180
However, Xia Song was colluded with Yang Huaimin

377
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:28,740
to detect news of the palace

378
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,540
with complete witnesses and evidence.

379
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:37,260
Yang Huaimin has been cast out,

380
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:39,220
same for Xia Song.

381
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:42,100
If it’s within your duty,

382
00:19:42,100 --> 00:19:43,140
you should continue the investigation.

383
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:45,420
But I have a word for you,

384
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:47,980
holding to just.

385
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,940
Don’t be radicalized by personal favors.

386
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:56,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

387
00:20:00,900 --> 00:20:02,140
Equal work and rest?

388
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:06,740
Why should Chen Zhizhong remain in the Capital?

389
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,380
You, a villain?

390
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:12,620
You are degrading?

391
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:15,140
I say, Chen Zhizhong’s family

392
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:17,420
is indeed a total mess.

393
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,940
Even if we expected that Wen Yanbo

394
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:26,380
was able to put down the insurgency
in Qinghe County.

395
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:32,220
It was unexpected of insurgency coming along

396
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,500
with disturbance in the palace.

397
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:38,100
All were related to Maitreya Sect,

398
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:41,420
but His Majesty didn’t care.

399
00:20:43,980 --> 00:20:45,420
Let go of the remnants.

400
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:48,300
Let go of the remnants.

401
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:52,580
Such a waste.

402
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:54,820
What a nice trap!

403
00:21:03,140 --> 00:21:04,980
What an insidious man Wen Yanbo is!

404
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,860
His wife

405
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:09,380
is close with us.

406
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:10,780
We thought we were a clique,

407
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:14,060
yet he blamed on you,

408
00:21:14,660 --> 00:21:16,740
pretending to be fair and modesty at court.

409
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:19,700
He benefited from it greatly,

410
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:20,780
with promotion to Vice Prime Minister.

411
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:23,980
What a hypocrite!

412
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:26,140
And Wang Gongchen...

413
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:27,220
Forget it.

414
00:21:29,940 --> 00:21:31,540
This move was...

415
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:38,500
Have some water.

416
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,860
I’m an old man

417
00:21:51,980 --> 00:21:53,420
with numbered days.

418
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:56,900
Don’t be like this.

419
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:04,460
I chose a risky move,

420
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:08,340
yet missed His Majesty.

421
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:14,820
But your illness...

422
00:22:17,260 --> 00:22:20,060
You can’t stand long travel.

423
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:25,260
My illness is in time.

424
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:29,380
His Majesty has sent an Imperial Physician

425
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,740
for me.

426
00:22:32,100 --> 00:22:34,660
I have submitted a proposal,
begging to stay in the Capital.

427
00:22:40,260 --> 00:22:41,940
You never know.

428
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:50,020
Lantiao remains in

429
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:52,060
the Pavilion of Luan.

430
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:54,540
If she gave birth to a boy,

431
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:58,020
he would be prince of Madam Zhang.

432
00:22:58,820 --> 00:23:01,500
His Majesty had the intention
to promote Madam Zhang.

433
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:03,980
Till then,

434
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:05,900
they could jointly

435
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:08,140
speak for Madam Zhang.

436
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:13,900
Then, everything would get better.

437
00:23:21,260 --> 00:23:23,220
His Majesty spared Xia Song
without stripping his honor

438
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,620
by listing crimes,

439
00:23:25,220 --> 00:23:27,660
yet he submitted a proposal to commit his crimes

440
00:23:28,140 --> 00:23:29,740
with a pleading to stay in the Capital
due to severe illness.

441
00:23:30,660 --> 00:23:31,660
Censor He was furious.

442
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:33,220
In the morning court yesterday,

443
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:34,860
he spoke to His Majesty,

444
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:36,780
scolding Xia Song as a shameless

445
00:23:38,060 --> 00:23:40,300
and degrading villain known to the whole country.

446
00:23:40,620 --> 00:23:41,700
Ousting him

447
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:42,700
is a pleasant event

448
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:44,100
in and outside the court.

449
00:23:44,460 --> 00:23:46,020
May His Majesty tough his heart this time.

450
00:23:46,580 --> 00:23:48,180
And he quoted Confucius’s teaching

451
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,060
on how to administer a country.

452
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:51,260
The teaching was,

453
00:23:51,260 --> 00:23:52,500
I couldn’t remember it.

454
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:54,740
Confucius said,

455
00:23:54,860 --> 00:23:57,100
banish the songs of Zheng,
and keep far from specious talkers.

456
00:23:58,220 --> 00:24:00,180
The songs of Zheng are licentious,
specious talkers are dangerous.

457
00:24:00,460 --> 00:24:02,500
To administer a country,
one should keep far from specious talkers.

458
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,900
With such men being besides the Emperor,

459
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:06,820
state affairs would be harmed.

460
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:09,020
Splendid!

461
00:24:09,540 --> 00:24:11,260
Princess is so knowledgeable.

462
00:24:12,580 --> 00:24:13,620
Huirou,

463
00:24:14,380 --> 00:24:15,180
why don’t you

464
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:16,700
read more poetry?

465
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:19,660
Girls learn to administer a country, what for?

466
00:24:20,780 --> 00:24:21,940
Whatever I learn is useless.

467
00:24:22,460 --> 00:24:23,700
Her Highness is knowledgeable,

468
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:24,780
graceful and rule-abiding,

469
00:24:24,860 --> 00:24:26,380
yet father only loves Madam Zhang.

470
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:27,660
For her,

471
00:24:27,660 --> 00:24:29,300
father even ignored Confucius’s words,

472
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:30,740
insisting on keeping a specious talker

473
00:24:30,740 --> 00:24:31,780
at his side

474
00:24:32,060 --> 00:24:33,900
only because this man could be back for her

475
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,060
and frame Her Highness up.

476
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:36,980
Father likes those who look

477
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:37,940
pretty himself.

478
00:24:38,140 --> 00:24:39,300
If others behave the same, however,

479
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:40,620
it is frivolity.

480
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:44,100
Your behavior is more inappropriate as you grow up.

481
00:24:44,820 --> 00:24:46,020
Go back to your room and reflect on your misdeed.

482
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:52,580
Madam.

483
00:24:53,980 --> 00:24:54,660
What’s…

484
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:57,100
What’s wrong with her?

485
00:25:02,380 --> 00:25:03,700
No need to hide it from you.

486
00:25:04,940 --> 00:25:05,980
It was because of

487
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,700
Her Highness’s nephew.

488
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:12,180
He’s as handsome as Adonis.

489
00:25:13,620 --> 00:25:14,620
But His Majesty

490
00:25:15,580 --> 00:25:16,660
doesn’t want her

491
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:18,060
to marry her dreamed boy.

492
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,260
Instead, he wants Huirou’s future husband

493
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,580
to adore her like a fairy.

494
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:27,340
It’s a parents’ wish.

495
00:25:28,620 --> 00:25:32,540
Cao Ping is too unrestrained.

496
00:25:33,780 --> 00:25:34,940
But Huirou believes that

497
00:25:34,940 --> 00:25:36,620
His Majesty doesn’t like the Caos,

498
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:39,820
so he wraps her up

499
00:25:40,980 --> 00:25:42,420
as if she were jewelry or jade ware

500
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:45,300
to glorify his mother’s family.

501
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:48,900
Honestly,

502
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:52,500
Huirou is not the only one who thinks so.

503
00:25:59,460 --> 00:26:00,180
Your Majesty,

504
00:26:00,220 --> 00:26:00,940
Your Majesty,

505
00:26:03,340 --> 00:26:04,020
Your Majesty!

506
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:05,860
I’ve submitted several proposals,

507
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:07,580
yet Your Majesty ignored them all.

508
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:09,300
I asked to see you in person,

509
00:26:09,540 --> 00:26:10,740
yet Your Majesty ignored as well.

510
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:12,180
I can only wait here.

511
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:13,420
If I ever alarmed Your Majesty,

512
00:26:13,420 --> 00:26:14,740
I’m willing to be at Your Majesty’s disposal.

513
00:26:15,940 --> 00:26:18,140
But please let me speak up.

514
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:21,100
I know what you want to say.

515
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:23,780
First things first,

516
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:25,180
Xia Song is very sick.

517
00:26:25,500 --> 00:26:26,220
He should…

518
00:26:26,580 --> 00:26:28,060
Xia Song is sly and cunning.

519
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,100
His casting out of the Capital

520
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:31,140
complies with the will of heaven and the people.

521
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:33,060
Your Majesty should make up your mind,

522
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,660
without any delay.

523
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:39,220
In the past, there was an official trying
to persuade the Emperor with his head broken,

524
00:26:39,740 --> 00:26:40,980
will you do the same as he did?

525
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:45,220
In the past,

526
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:48,620
the Emperor didn’t take advice,
so the official had to break his head.

527
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:51,860
Now, Your Majesty takes advice wisely,

528
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:55,060
how could I value my name

529
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:57,180
and make the Emperor guilty.

530
00:27:15,140 --> 00:27:16,900
I won’t be able to come back this time.

531
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,420
In this life,

532
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,180
I was poor,

533
00:27:23,900 --> 00:27:24,660
and became rich;

534
00:27:26,020 --> 00:27:27,260
I was loyal and brave,

535
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:31,180
and became evil.

536
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:38,700
I’ve longed to be a senior official,

537
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:40,340
to grow old with a dear wife.

538
00:27:42,140 --> 00:27:43,540
In the end,

539
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:46,100
I realize

540
00:27:48,060 --> 00:27:51,580
the meaning of unresolved longing.

541
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:58,140
Zhang Maoze has found out a lot.

542
00:27:59,580 --> 00:28:00,860
As for smuggling salt,

543
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,900
he’s unlikely to collect the evidence completely.

544
00:28:07,580 --> 00:28:09,260
It’s not a matter of murder and treason

545
00:28:09,780 --> 00:28:11,420
and doesn’t affect military affairs.

546
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:13,540
With incomplete evidence,

547
00:28:13,540 --> 00:28:14,780
I won’t be punished heavily

548
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:15,860
according to His Majesty’s personality.

549
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,100
His Majesty

550
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:22,940
would rather pardon a suspected one

551
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:24,820
than to punish an innocent one.

552
00:28:36,980 --> 00:28:40,300
He won’t be hard on you.

553
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:41,820
However,

554
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:47,780
as for promoting Madam Zhang

555
00:28:49,340 --> 00:28:50,940
is impossible anyway.

556
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:55,460
As for Lantiao,

557
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:58,980
I believe she would immediately

558
00:28:58,980 --> 00:29:00,380
play up to the Empress.

559
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:06,420
Yulan, alas.

